ederal officers in Jordan, Montana.", :date=>"1996-03-25", :category=>"Economy", :location=>"Jordan, Montana"}, {:lat=>nil, :lng=>nil, :people=>"Whoopi Goldberg,Dorothy Chandler Pavilion,Los Angeles,Best Picture", :description=>"The 68th Academy Awards, hosted by Whoopi Goldberg, are held at the Dorothy Chandler Pavilion in Los Angeles, California with Braveheart winning Best Picture.", :date=>"1996-03-25", :category=>"Cultural", :location=>"by Whoopi Goldberg"}, {:lat=>nil, :lng=>nil, :people=>"International Monetary Fund", :description=>"The International Monetary Fund approves a $10.2 billion loan to Russia for economic reform.", :date=>"1996-03-26", :category=>"Economy", :location=>"Russia for economic reform"}, {:lat=>106.792999, :lng=>-6.589166, :people=>"Pasar Anyar,West Java", :description=>"Fire breaks out at the Pasar Anyar shopping centre in Bogor, West Java. The first death toll estimate is 78 until rescuers notice that 68 of them are mannequins.", :date=>"1996-03-28", :category=>"Crime", :location=>"Bogor, West Java The first death toll estimate is 78 until rescuers notice that 68 of them are mannequins"}, {:lat=>nil, :lng=>nil, :people=>"Louise Jensen,Allan Ford,Justin Fowler,Geoffrey Pernell", :description=>"Three British soldiers are found guilty of the manslaughter of Danish tour guide Louise Jensen in Cyprus. Allan Ford, Justin Fowler and Geoffrey Pernell receive life sentences for their crime, which was committed in September 1994.", :date=>"1996-03-28", :category=>"Crime", :location=>"Cyprus Allan Ford"}, {:lat=>-62.6571885, :lng=>44.6922613, :people=>"Halifax Regional Municipality,Nova Scotia", :description=>"The Halifax Regional Municipality in Nova Scotia is created.", :date=>"1996-04-01", :category=>"Cultural", :location=>"Nova Scotia"}, {:lat=>-74.4532954, :lng=>18.4055787, :people=>"", :description=>"An overcrowded ferry sinks off the coast of Irois, Haiti, killing more than 200 people.", :date=>"1996-04-01", :category=>"Accidents", :locati